Analyst & Investor Day, 2017




Oyu Tolgoi: Made in Mongolia








Turquoise Hill Resources is an international mining company focused 
on copper, gold and coal mines in the Asia Pacific region.
Principal asset:
A 66% interest in Oyu Tolgoi, one of the world's largest copper-gold-silver mines now producing and shipping concentrate to customers in China.






















